  TAI LIEU RA SOAT THUAT TOAN PROJECT IOT-SMARTHOME-ELDERLY
  Ngay cap nhat: 2026-05-06
  Pham vi: Ma nguon hien co trong workspace (backend la noi chua thuat toan chinh)

============================================================
  1) TOM TAT NHANH
============================================================
  Project co cac nhom thuat toan sau:

  A. Rule-based decision (nguong va logic dieu kien): CO
  B. Machine Learning (anomaly + classification): CO
  C. Time-series preprocessing va feature engineering: CO
  D. Tinh toan tin hieu y sinh HRV: CO
  E. NLP/Intent parsing cho tro ly AI: CO (rule + LLM parser)
  F. Frontend/Mobile co thuat toan AI rieng: KHONG thay thay ro trong source app

  Ket luan tong quan:
- Day la he thong lai (hybrid): Rule-based + ML + phan tich y sinh + scheduler theo thoi gian.
- Cac thuat toan duoc trien khai va goi trong runtime, khong chi nam trong tai lieu.

============================================================
  2) THUAT TOAN CHINH VA CHUC NANG
============================================================
  2.1 Tier 1 - Rule-based Heart Rate Risk
  Muc dich:
- Danh gia muc nguy co tuc thi dua tren BPM.

  Logic:
- BPM >= 130  -> emergency
- BPM >= 100  -> warning_high
- BPM < 50    -> warning_low
- Con lai     -> normal

  Vi tri code:
- backend/app/ai/services/heart_rate_ai.py

  Y nghia:
- Lop bao ve co ban, phan ung nhanh, khong phu thuoc model.

------------------------------------------------------------
  2.2 Tier 2 - Anomaly Detection (IsolationForest)
  Muc dich:
- Phat hien mau du lieu bat thuong (outlier) khong can nhan.

  Mo hinh:
- sklearn.ensemble.IsolationForest

  Input runtime:
- HeartRateMonitor tao vector 7 feature context: heart_rate, room_temp, humidity, light_level, hour, is_night, is_dark
- Sau do AnomalyDetector uu tien mo hinh HR-only neu loader co anomaly_hr_scaler.pkl
- Neu khong co anomaly_hr_scaler thi fallback sang X_scaled day du

  Output:
- model.predict(...) == -1  -> anomaly
- model.predict(...) == 1   -> normal

  Vi tri code:
- Train tong quat: backend/app/ai/training/train_pipeline.py
- Infer: backend/app/ai/inference/anomaly_detector.py
- Huong tune/evaluate HR-only: backend/tune_and_retrain_anomaly.py, backend/evaluate_anomaly_model.py

  Ghi chu ky thuat:
- contamination doc tu env ANOMALY_CONTAMINATION cho pipeline train tong quat.
- Runtime hien tai ho tro ca fallback full-feature va nhanh HR-only uu tien neu model/scaler HR da duoc load.

------------------------------------------------------------
  2.3 Tier 3 - HRV Analysis (Heart Rate Variability)
  Muc dich:
- Danh gia bien thien nhip tim nguoi cao tuoi theo cua so truot.

  Thuat toan tinh toan:
- Chuyen BPM -> RR interval (ms): RR = 60000 / BPM
- Mean RR: trung binh RR
- SDNN: do lech chuan cua RR
- RMSSD: can bac hai trung binh binh phuong sai khac lien tiep RR
- pNN50: ty le (%) sai khac lien tiep RR > 50ms

  Cua so va nguong:
- WINDOW_SIZE = 60 mau
- MIN_SAMPLES = 5
- RMSSD_VERY_LOW = 10 ms
- RMSSD_LOW = 15 ms
- SDNN_LOW = 20 ms
- PNN50_LOW = 3%

  Risk level:
- very_low_hrv: rmssd < 10 hoac sdnn < 20
- low_hrv: rmssd < 15 hoac pnn50 < 3
- normal: con lai

  Vi tri code:
- backend/app/ai/services/hrv_analyzer.py
- Duoc goi trong backend/app/ai/services/heart_rate_ai.py

------------------------------------------------------------
  2.4 Mood Classification (RandomForestClassifier)
  Muc dich:
- Du doan trang thai/mood tu bo feature da chuan hoa.

  Mo hinh:
- sklearn.ensemble.RandomForestClassifier

  Nhan training:
- Tao nhan mood qua ham _calc_mood (rule labeling) trong pipeline train.

  Output infer:
- Tra ve label mood tu model; fallback "VIGILANT" neu model chua san sang.

  Vi tri code:
- Train: backend/app/ai/training/train_pipeline.py
- Infer: backend/app/ai/inference/mood_predictor.py

------------------------------------------------------------
  2.5 Automation Classification (RandomForestClassifier)
  Muc dich:
- Du doan hanh dong tu dong hoa (action_label).

  Mo hinh:
- sklearn.ensemble.RandomForestClassifier

  Nhan training:
- action_label duoc gan tu ControlLog, canh cua so thoi gian 2 phut.

  Output infer:
- action label du doan; fallback "NO_ACTION" neu model chua san sang.

  Vi tri code:
- Train: backend/app/ai/training/train_pipeline.py
- Infer: backend/app/ai/inference/automation_predictor.py
- Tao dataset: backend/app/ai/training/dataset_builder.py

------------------------------------------------------------
  2.6 Feature Engineering va Data Alignment
  Muc dich:
- Chuan hoa dau vao cho train/infer, dam bao thu tu cot va chat luong du lieu.

  Ky thuat:
- Add hour tu timestamp (hoac gio he thong trong realtime)
- is_night = 1 neu gio >= 20 hoac <= 6
- is_dark = 1 neu light_level < 50
- Pivot theo sensor code, forward fill, resample 5 phut, mean, dropna
- finalize_features: bo sung cot thieu, ep so, fill NaN, sap xep dung thu tu FEATURE_COLUMNS

  Vi tri code:
- backend/app/ai/data/feature_engineering.py
- backend/app/ai/training/dataset_builder.py
- backend/app/ai/config.py

------------------------------------------------------------
  2.7 Rule Engine cho Automation Condition (Scheduler)
  Muc dich:
- Kich hoat hanh dong tu dong hoa dua tren dieu kien cau hinh DB.

  Cach lam:
- Parse chuoi dieu kien bang regex an toan (khong dung eval).
- Ho tro mau: value > 35, value == 'ON', is_on == true...
- Mapping toan tu: ==, !=, >, >=, <, <=
- Chay interval 30s de kiem tra dieu kien.

  Vi tri code:
- backend/app/scheduler.py

------------------------------------------------------------
  2.8 NLP Intent Parsing (Hybrid Rule + LLM)
  Muc dich:
- Trich xuat intent dieu khien/query/chat tu cau lenh nguoi dung.

  Co che:
- Rule-based parser uu tien truoc (keyword + regex room/floor/device).
- Neu rule khong match -> goi LLM (Ollama) de parse JSON intent.

  Vi tri code:
- backend/app/ai/services/ai_service.py

  Luu y:
- Day la thuat toan xu ly ngon ngu/ra quyet dinh, khong phai model train trong project.

============================================================
  3) LUONG CHAY THUAT TOAN THUC TE (RUNTIME)
============================================================
  Luon tim thay duong goi runtime cho phan AI tim mach:

  1. MQTT listener nhan BPM tu topic heart_rate
  2. Lay boi canh sensor gan nhat (room_temp, humidity, light_level)
  3. Goi HeartRateMonitor.on_bpm_update(...)
  4. Trong monitor:
   - Cap nhat HRV analyzer (tier 3)
   - Danh gia nguong BPM rule-based (tier 1)
   - Neu co scaler/model -> anomaly + mood (tier 2)
   - Nham muc risk neu anomaly/HRV bat thuong
   - Phat alert qua socket + luu DB

  Vi tri code quan trong:
- backend/app/gateways/mqtt_listener.py
- backend/app/ai/services/heart_rate_ai.py
- backend/app/ai/inference/model_loader.py

============================================================
  4) CAC MODEL FILE DANG DUOC QUAN LY
============================================================
  Thu muc: backend/app/ai/models/

- anomaly_model.pkl
- anomaly_hr_scaler.pkl
- automation_model.pkl
- mood_model.pkl
- scaler.pkl

  ModelLoader se load cac model nay khi khoi dong backend.
  Neu thieu file, he thong fallback o mot so nhanh (vd mood/anomaly).

============================================================
  5) THAM SO/CAU HINH QUAN TRONG
============================================================
- ANOMALY_CONTAMINATION (env): ti le outlier cho IsolationForest
- FEATURE_COLUMNS (co dinh):
    heart_rate, room_temp, humidity, light_level, hour, is_night, is_dark
- ALERT_COOLDOWN_SEC = 30 (giam spam alert)
- HRV window/threshold nhu muc 2.3

============================================================
  6) DANH GIA CHAT LUONG THUAT TOAN (THEO SOURCE HIEN TAI)
============================================================
  Diem manh:
- Kien truc hybrid 3 tang: rule + ML + HRV
- Co fallback khi model/scaler khong san sang
- Feature order duoc co dinh ro rang, giam loi mismatch train/infer
- Condition evaluator an toan (regex), tranh nguy co eval injection

  Diem can luu y:
- Mood/automation labels co phan sinh tong hop va rule-labeling -> can theo doi drift
- Dataset real co the it, dang bo sung synthetic trong giai doan dau
- Can quy trinh danh gia model dinh ky (precision/recall/anomaly false positive)

============================================================
  7) CAC THUAT TOAN KHONG THAY TRIEN KHAI AI RIENG
============================================================
- Frontend: chu yeu UI/state/socket, khong thay model ML suy luan tai client.
- Mobile app (ma nguon lib): khong thay khoi AI anomaly/HRV training/predict rieng.

============================================================
  8) KET LUAN CUOI CUNG
============================================================
  Project CO thuat toan va CO dang van hanh:

  1) Rule-based threshold cho nhip tim
  2) IsolationForest anomaly detection
  3) RandomForest mood classification
  4) RandomForest automation classification
  5) HRV metrics (RMSSD, SDNN, pNN50, Mean RR)
  6) Feature engineering time-series + standardization
  7) Rule engine scheduler dieu kien tu dong hoa
  8) Hybrid NLP intent parsing (rule + LLM)

  Tai lieu nay duoc tong hop truc tiep tu source code hien co de phuc vu bao cao do an.

